snippet.title: Rada Quest: Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Rada Quest is an online multiplayer trading card strategy game developed by 3DK Render a Block producer guild for the WAX blockchain. Players will gather resources through the construction and upgrading of their buildings. The main goal of the game is that players can fight each other online and resolve quests by using their high-value cards (NFTs) supported by a boost system.

Website: https://radaquest.net
Game: https://game.radaquest.net
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/3dkrender
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RadaQuestTCG
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/radaquest/
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/radaquesttcg/
Whitepaper: https://radaquest.net/whitepaper/
